[AutoPilot L2 Up On/L2 Down Off]
author=47iscool
description=Here is my version, this one allows you to gain A-SPEC points
as well as mileage.
Only enable/disable in a race, because it wiill freeze the game if used in the menus.
I suggest using the tires cheat when using this code. Why? Well if you use this code
at the pit stop the AI may keep driving in the pit each & every lap.

One more thing,
if you turn it on before the car drives past the finish line at the start of the race the game will disable it. Simply re-enable it if this occurs.
patch=1,EE,203A4BC0,extended,3C010000
