[Disable Parts Change (L2 Up On/L2 Down Off)]
author=47iscool
description=
I Prefer Using R5 Racing Tires Since They Have Better Grip.
Alongside That I Use The Always Good Tires Code. Some Events
Will Automatically Change Your Tires To S3 (or Dirt) Depending On The Event.
This Stops Any/All Parts From Being Changed Out Of Your Car(s)
patch=1,EE,D086F99C,extended,0000FEEF
patch=1,EE,2014048C,extended,00000000
patch=1,EE,D086F99C,extended,0000FEBF
patch=1,EE,2014048C,extended,0C1102D4

[Disable Rearview Mirror]
author=47iscool
description=Recommended to be used when using "cockpit view" code, also works just fine on it's own.
patch=1,EE,2037AEC8,extended,24630000

[Disable Rev Limiter]
author=47iscool
description=Your car will no longer back down at it's original top speed. Enjoy!

patch=1,EE,2035542C,extended,1000000A

[Disable/Enable Championship R1 Up On/R1 Down Off]
author=47iscool
description=Only Use When In a Championship.
Enabling this when you are not in a championship, and choosing yes to continue
will result in a freeze. This reason for this code is to allow you to temporarily disable
the championship so you can modify and/or change the car you are driving.
patch=1,EE,D064C794,extended,0000F7EF
patch=1,EE,00A44AB0,extended,00000000
patch=1,EE,D064C794,extended,0000F7BF
patch=1,EE,00A44AB0,extended,00000001

[Disable/Enable Spoiler-Wing L2 Up/L2 Down]
author=47iscool
description=Notes: 
1. Only enable at the race setup screen and disable while in any other 
menus or garage or it will freeze. Only works on this screen and while in a race.
2. Only works on cars that have a replaceable spoiler-wing.
3. The car must have it's original wing-spoiler and an aftermarket one.

patch=1,EE,D064C794,extended,0000FEEF
