[Fast Car Part(s) Install From Tune Shops (READ NOTE)]
author=47iscool
description=I always disliked the delay when installing parts that was introduced in GT4.
This removes that, while also, and this wasn't on purpose, almost instantly shows the prize cars when completing a championship even before the drum roll finishes.
May cause issues in Arcade Mode.
patch=1,EE,204A2324,extended,20522F10

