[Garage Slot 1 Car 4WD/AWD (Press Select+R3)]
author=47iscool
description=This Will Make The Car In Garage Slot 1 4WD/AWD
Using The Parts Setting From The Subaru Impreza STi
Torque Split In The VCD Is Set To Front Wheels 50%/Rear Wheels 50%.
In The Parts Menu When Go To VCD It Will Say The VCD
Is Only Standard But It's There, You Can Adjust It On Your Own.
Whenever You Get Into A Car It Is
Set In Slot 1 In Your Garage.
patch=1,EE,E003FFFA,extended,0086F99C
patch=1,EE,10A1F810,extended,00000A34
patch=1,EE,10A1F8FC,extended,00000F3C
patch=1,EE,00A1F8FE,extended,00000032

