[Press L1+L2 For Transmission Final Drive at 2000 (Garage Slot Car 1)]
author=47iscool
description=Whenever you get into a car it is set in slot 1. This even works with stock transmissions.
It allow most cars to reach 240-400 MPH or more depending on the car.
Although cars with low HP will be more sluggish.
